---
import AboutHeroImage from '../assets/blog-placeholder-about.jpg';
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About Me"
	description="Learn more about Locch and their journey"
	pubDate={new Date('January 24 2026')}
	heroImage={AboutHeroImage}
>
	<h2>Hi, I'm Locch!</h2>
	
	<p>
		Welcome to my corner of the internet! I'm a passionate developer and technology enthusiast 
		who loves building things, learning new skills, and sharing knowledge with others.
	</p>

	<p>
		This blog is my digital garden where I document my journey, share what I'm working on, 
		and explore ideas that excite me. I believe in the power of continuous learning and the 
		importance of giving back to the community through open source and knowledge sharing.
	</p>

	<h3>What I'm Passionate About</h3>
	<ul>
		<li>Machine learning and software engineering</li>
		<li>Building performant, user-friendly applications</li>
		<li>Exploring new technologies and programming paradigms</li>
		<li>Contributing to open source projects</li>
		<li>Writing clean, maintainable code</li>
	</ul>

	<p>
		When I'm not coding, you can find me reading tech blogs, experimenting with side projects, 
		or enjoying a good cup of coffee while thinking about the next big idea.
	</p>

	<h3>Let's Connect!</h3>
	<p>
		I'm always excited to connect with fellow developers and tech enthusiasts. 
		Feel free to reach out if you'd like to collaborate on a project, discuss ideas, 
		or just say hello!
	</p>

	<p>
		Thanks for taking the time to learn a bit more about me. I hope you find my blog 
		helpful and inspiring. Happy coding!
	</p>
</Layout>
